messages.title: Hello,
messages.content: We called to see you today along with your local Labour Team, to speak to you about any local concerns affecting you. The elections coming up will be really close and your vote is vital!

contactInformation.address: Promoted by Bill Knowles on behalf of Chris Mole and Mary Blake and printed by Suffolk Labour Print all of 33 Silent Street, Ipswich IP1 1TF
